INSERT INTO `worklist` VALUES (50, '软件开发工程师-java方向', 10, '小米', '3', '深圳', '10000', '8小时', '互联网', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">任职要求：</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1、熟练掌握Java编程语言，熟悉Linux开发环境；</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2、熟悉Web服务开发，了解Web服务框架，了解Web安全；</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3、扎实的编程能力，熟悉常用算法和数据结构，掌握常用的设计模式；</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4、了解常见的分布式存储计算框架；</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5、有强烈的上进心和自我驱动，学习适应能力强，乐观自信，能挑战自我不断追求卓越。</span></p>', '2259410812@qq.com', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">岗位描述：</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1、负责相关业务服务器端的研发工作，包括需求沟通、功能设计与开发等；</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2、负责相关业务服务器相关的高并发架构设计、线上维护、性能调优等；</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3、和产品/测试/运营进行密切沟通，能够根据需求提出合理技术方案；</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4、负责软件开发过程中的问题分析和总结，提供建议和帮助改善研发流程。</span></p>');
