<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">岗位职责：</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1. 根据需求文档，编写测试用例，独立完成交付的测试任务</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2. 用例执行过程中，能快速、准确的定位问题，并进行反馈</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, verdana, helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, STHeitiSC-Light, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3. 及时反馈游戏bug，跟进bug修复，并总结经验，持续提升项目产出质量</span></p>');
